arts.ttl: Arsenal secure crucial WCL win at Juve to stay unbeaten under Slegers
arts.sum: Arsenal secured what could be a pivotal win in Group C of the Women's Champions League, thrashing Serie A leaders Juventus 4-0 in Turin to stay unbeaten under interim head coach Renee Slegers.

arts.ttl: Breath of fresh air – Beth Mead says Arsenal enjoying life under Renee Slegers
arts.sum: Slegers was handed the caretaker reins at the Gunners after last month’s resignation of Jonas Eidevall.
